review:
My Mother has been Diabetic for past 10+ years. All these years she converted from Medicine to Insulin patient and her dosage had increased to 140 units per day. This was very alarming to us and we decided to change her doctor as we were not seeing any results even with diet control.
We researched about Dr. Indumathi Kuberan online and just took a chance. I was completely overwhelmed by her response to a first time patient. 
She almost spent 40-50 min with us while other patients were waiting for their turn. She gave every minute details about how she plans to reduce my mom's diabetes and eventually bring her back to medicines only by completely removing insulin support. Its just one month with Dr. Indumathi but I am confident that we will achieve what we have planned for my mother. And even if we don't end up eliminating insulin completely, We have extensively reduced it to 28 units already. 
I had not met a Doctor before who will go such great lengths for a patient. I will recommend Dr. Indumathi to any diabetic patient in Mumbai.
